text:
Twitter Is Losing Its Damn Mind Over Beyoncé's Pregnancy Announcement 
#BeyonceIsPregnant By Emily Tannenbaum Feb 1, 2017 Beyoncé posted her gorgeous pregnancy announcement photo 30 minutes ago and the world has already lost its damn mind. The picture has 1,427,371 likes and over 100,000 comments at press time. #BeyonceIsPregnant, Beyoncé, and #Twins are all trending on Twitter. These twins have given us life and hope where there was none just an hour ago. A photo posted by Beyoncé (@beyonce) on Feb 1, 2017 at 10:39am PST   The Internet will never be the same: Half a million Tweets about @Beyonce 's surprise #twins announcement. It's been 45 minutes. (Spiked at 17k Tweets per min.)  
— Twitter Data (@TwitterData) February 1, 2017 NOT #FAKENEWS 
— bey tá gravidaaaa (@AG_roby) February 1, 2017 Most Popular
